import React from 'react'
import {Navbar,Nav,Container} from 'react-bootstrap'
const Home = (props) => {
    return (
        <Container>
        <Navbar expand="lg" variant="light" bg="light">
          <Container>
            <Navbar.Brand href="#">Navbar</Navbar.Brand>
          </Container>
        </Navbar>
      </Container>
    )
}

export default Home
